title: War of the Roses: His Dead Ex Girlfriend Texted Him
description: Riley was hanging out with her boyfriend and they were looking at his phone when he got a text from his ex girlfriend.  The part that's super strange, she passed away.  We bring in Gary Spivey for some help on this one and found out if the text really came from his ex that passed away.
